&lt;li&gt;Has no connection to our ideology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Was chosen by our opponents to insult and humiliate us.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is our right, not our opponents', to decide the terminology that represents us the best.&lt;/p&gt;
